fiftyone.mobile.detection.trie
Class FiftyOneMapper

java.lang.Object
  fiftyone.mobile.detection.trie.FiftyOneMapper

public class FiftyOneMapper
extends Object

Due to the size of the Trie tree structure, the data cannot fit into a single ByteBuffer. Therefore, this class is used to wrap the file channel and and become logically one channel.

Version:
2.2.9.1
Author:
51Degrees.mobi
